The following series were filmed by the Genealogical Society of Utah and are available for use through . Film numbers are shown in the . The easiest access is through an "Author" search on "Judd, Sylvester" and then selecting the appropriate "Connecticut Archives" series.
Civil Officers, 1st series, 1669-1756; Colonial Wars, 1st series, 1675-1775; Colonial Wars, 2nd series, 1689-1806; Ecclesiastical Affairs, 1st series, 1658-1789;
Indians, 1st series, 1647-1789; Lotteries and Divorces, 1st series, 1755-1789; Lotteries and Divorces, 2nd, 1718-1820; Militia, 1st series, 1678-1757; Militia, 2nd series, 1747-1786; Militia, 3rd series, 1728-1820; Revolutionary War, 1st series, 1763-1789;
Revolutionary War, 2nd series, 1756-1856; Revolutionary War, 3rd series, 1765-1820; Susquehanna Settlers 1755-1796 and Western Lands 1783-1789, 1st series; War of 1812. 1812-1819.
